Privacy Policy for LinkedIn Grabber Extension

Last Updated: 7/25/2024

1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how the LinkedIn Grabber Extension ("we", "our", or "the Extension") collects, uses, and protects information when you use our browser extension. We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected.

2. Information We Collect

The Extension collects the following anonymous data:

a) Usage Data: We track when the Extension is opened and used.
b) Geographical Location: With your permission, we collect your approximate geographical location (latitude and longitude) when you use the Extension.
c) Lead Count: We keep a count of the number of leads you've pushed to HubSpot using our Extension.

3. How We Use the Information

We use this information solely for the purpose of:

a) Understanding how our Extension is being used.
b) Improving the functionality and user experience of our Extension.
c) Analyzing geographical distribution of our users.

4. Data Storage and Security

The lead count is stored locally on your device. Usage data and geographical location are sent to Google Analytics, which adheres to its own privacy policy (available at https://policies.google.com/privacy).

We do not collect or store any personal information, LinkedIn profile data, or HubSpot data.

5. Third-Party Services

We use Google Analytics to process the collected data. Google Analytics is compliant with GDPR and offers data anonymization features. For more information, please refer to Google's Privacy Policy.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to opt-out of location tracking at any time by adjusting your browser settings. However, this may affect some functionalities of the Extension.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

By using the LinkedIn Grabber Extension, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
